					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I really should change my tutorial. This is a bit 'cargo cult' programming. Changing the PPU Address isn't necessary to set the scroll. Properly, the nametable selection should be a write to 2000 and then only 2 writes to 2005 (scroll) are required.</div>

					
