						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Not sure what 2000 has to do with it.</div><br /><br />From the wiki on Register 2000, the bits are<br /><br />VPHB SINN<br /><br />NMI enable (V), PPU master/slave (P), sprite height (H), background tile select (B), sprite tile select (S), increment mode (I), nametable select (NN)<br /><br />Writing to the 2 lowest bits changes which nametable is rendered.</div>

					
